22175.description: MP +37, Resistance to Bleed +30%, Bleed attack rate +30%, heal amount +15%, vampiric rage effect, Resistance to Shock/Metal attacks +30%, Shock/Metal attack rate +30%, and Resistance to Dark +15. Only one effect is applied even when the same two earrings are worn. If it is equipped together with a standard Earring of Zaken, only the effect of Blessed Earring of Zaken will be applied. Earring of Zaken

22176.name: Angry Bunny Lure Scroll - Event
22176.description: Scroll that summons an Angry Bunny. If you rid the bunny of it's anger you can acquire Apiga. (De-rageifying is only possible through Bunny Pacifier Juice or Extra Strength Bunny Pacifier Juice.)

22177.name: Fearless Angry Bunny Lure Scroll - Event
22177.description: Scroll that summons a Fearless Angry Bunny. Sometimes after a Fearless Angry Bunny has been calmed down it can sometimes becomes a Raging Bunny. (De-rageifying is only possible through Bunny Pacifier Juice or Extra Strength Bunny Pacifier Juice.)

22178.name: Large Angry Bunny Lure Scroll - Event
22178.description: Scroll that summons a Large Angry Bunny. If you rid the bunny of its anger you can acquire Apiga or Golden Apiga. (De-rageifying is only possible through Bunny Pacifier Juice or Improved Bunny Pacifier Juice.)

22179.name: Large Fearless Bunny Lure Scroll - Event
22179.description: Scroll that summons a Large Fearless Angry Bunny. Sometimes after a Large Fearless Angry Bunny has been calmed down it can sometimes becomes a Large Raging Bunny. (De-rageifying is only possible through Bunny Pacifier Juice or Improved Bunny Pacifier Juice.)

22180.name: Bunny Anger Management Kit - Event
22180.description: An event pack that can be obtained once every 12 hours per account. If you double click it, you will obtain lure scrolls and bunny pacifier juices that are needed for the event. Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be stored in a private warehouse.

22181.name: Bunny Pacifier Juice - Event
22181.description: Effective when used on an Angry Bunny to relieve it of it's anger.

22182.name: Improved Bunny Pacifier Juice - Event
22182.description: Effective when used on an Angry Bunny to relieve it of it's anger. New and improved formula. Now stronger and acts quicker than the original.
